channel.title: How do you add objects (bank booths)
channel.description: Where do you go to add bank booths or any other objects? I go to objects.cfg and add it, but it doesnt show up. How do you do it?

item.title: How do you add objects (bank booths)
item.dc:creator: @Newb_2341 Newb 2341
item.description:
@Newb_2341 wrote:

[code]public class GlobalHandler {

public void makeGlobalObject(int x, int y, int typeID, int orientation, int tileObjectType){
for (Player p : server.playerHandler.players){
if(p != null){
client person = (client)p;
if((person.playerName != null || person.playerName != “null”)){
if(person.distanceToPoint(x, y) <= 60){
person.createNewTileObject(x, y, typeID, orientation, tileObjectType);
}
}
}
}
}

// 0 = WEST | -1 = NORTH | -2 = EAST | -3 = SOUTH
public void NewObjects() {
/* makeGlobalObject(3268, 3351, 1276, 0, 10); */
}
}[/code]
